Package: conky-manager
Version: 2.0.3
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-tk, conky, git
Maintainer: taghouti <taghouti@users.noreply.github.com>
Description: Conky Manager - Theme Manager for Conky
 A full-featured Python Conky Theme Manager with GUI.
 Features include theme discovery, switching, archive import,
 autostart configuration, layout editor, and auto-update.
